{"tid":2019131,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Kris Lau 無罪釋放！Plan Z重出江湖？","createTime":"2020-05-16T05:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T11:37:01.000Z","uid":54870,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ee950a414312cf4d58bf5c1a04f05a4716db8b9b","tid":2019131,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:21:10.000Z","msg":"補習導師涉賄評卷助理罪名不成立　裁判官：僥倖脫罪<br />\n<br />\n現代教育英文科補習導師劉冠華涉嫌於3年前，以1000元賄賂其出任考評局評卷助理的前學生黃子軒，以獲取文憑試英文科試卷三的機密資料，二人同被控一項串謀代理人接受利益罪。西九龍裁判法院裁判官梁少玲今早裁定二人罪名不成立，但形容是「僥倖脫罪」。梁少玲表示，本案關鍵在於劉冠華是否有意圖而行賄。根據案情，黃子軒早於2017年4月中透過手機通訊軟件錄音，向劉冠華分享評卷時見到的現象，例如很多人串錯字等，劉冠華事後才吩咐黃子軒在社交網站撰寫帖文「列點寫出改卷時見到的現象」，並提及會有報酬，該帖文同月下旬才發佈，明顯劉冠華在付錢予黃子軒前，已取得相關機密資料。對於該1000元是否劉冠華漏露機密資料的誘因存有疑點，亦沒有證據顯示劉冠華是串謀犯案。另外，控方不能證明劉冠華知悉黃子軒是考評局代理人，亦不能證明帖文內容是機密資料，基於疑點利益歸於被告，裁定二人罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過梁少玲強調，兩名被告自辯作供反覆、含糊、不可靠。黃子軒在案中的角色顯然符合「代理人」的定義，他清楚知悉考評局任用信的內容，不可能不知道帖文內容是機密資料，因此他確實有違反保密要求。當黃子軒將機密資料寫成帖文後，劉冠華將之發佈在社交網站，並給予黃子軒1000元作為報酬，黃子軒顯然有作為代理人而收受利益。梁少玲指，二人的行為「並非可疑這麼簡單」，只是未有證據證明他們的犯案意圖。<br />\n<br />\n2020-05-16 12:29:31"},{"pid":"df868821c4a384041dd2c715e2297beb08f46cde","tid":2019131,"uid":54870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:22:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526534-20200516.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526534-20200516.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BdqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=fbdfea82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526534-20200516.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6b44b34b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526534-20200516.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hNPt3af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhNPt3af.jpg&h=0189c641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裁判官宣判時指，控方不能證明劉冠華（圖）知悉黃子軒是考評局代理人。（港台圖片）"},{"pid":"f3d575a4230b75595dc671968c9ed741a9b6de85","tid":2019131,"uid":117834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:25:11.000Z","msg":"1000$真定假呀"},{"pid":"e3f21ec7b7a74e82845a907047c983ea2591cf8f","tid":2019131,"uid":175002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:31:03.000Z","msg":"補全科<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54a37d31bfa0e3daec23c19b9386dbbdaf4fa20","tid":2019131,"uid":346084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"冇得陪蕭源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35fb1f53dc3367d98bdfe909102ef1662787850","tid":2019131,"uid":310933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:46:42.000Z","msg":"成50歲都戇鳩鳩咁"},{"pid":"87d69e66cfcf210e4ae1622b3cfdac32adca655b","tid":2019131,"uid":199261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"咪害個細路啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d331d76d467ad6a6f24aabd70f7bf7ac40a1025","tid":2019131,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T07:33:21.000Z","msg":"$1000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b7648690a35ef11f9aa70897ce1b12f7c44e01","tid":2019131,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:01:36.000Z","msg":"正 又有得補牙kris<br />\n全科五星星不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ea4a74383577b755f06e4d50194a347bb63f56","tid":2019131,"uid":78703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:42:56.000Z","msg":"個黃子軒應該比條補習佬搞到唔洗考政府"},{"pid":"eca26da783830c190b59e7c33a2a29d746775937","tid":2019131,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31ea4a74383577b755f06e4d50194a347bb63f56","tid"